|---------------------------------------------------|
|  Syntax       |  Description                      |
|---------------+-----------------------------------|
|  install or i |  install <package-name>           |
|  remove or r  |  remove <package-name>            |
|  sync or u    |  to update/sync distro repository |
|  upgrade      |  to upgrade all of package        |
|  clean-cache  |  Clean up all local caches        |
|---------------+-----------------------------------|
|  man-ccli     |  view manual for ccli             |
|---------------------------------------------------|